    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>
                        <persName ref="#people/225" key="#Offersio/donatio #Count"
                            >Ildibrando</persName> in Dei nomine <rs key="#Count">comes</rs>, filio
                            <persName ref="#people/3307">bone memorie Eribrandi</persName>, offre
                        pro anima Deo et ecclesie beati <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/68"
                            key="#Domus">Sancti Martini</orgName>, <rs key="#Domus">domus
                            episcoporum</rs> sita hic Luca, idest <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casa et res</rs> mea illa, quas abeo in
                            <placeName ref="#places/2109"
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Fiscal_property #Object #Allocation_to_churches #Agricultural_workers #Count"
                            >loco Segio</placeName>, ubi reside <persName
                            key="#Agricultural_workers"><name ref="Martinulus"
                            >Martinulo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Agricultural_workers">massario</rs>; casa vero ipsa cum fundamento
                        et omne edeficio suo curte, orto, terris, vineis, virgareis, pratis, pascuis
                        (…). Pena in duplum. (…) Actum <placeName ref="#places/4" key="#Domus"
                            >Luca</placeName>. Scrive: <persName key="#Writer #Witness #Notary"
                                ><name ref="Imelfredus">Himalfridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Teudebertus">Teupertus</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Iohannes">Ioannes</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Georgius"
                            >Georgius</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Notary"><name
                                ref="Adalbertus">Adalpertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness #Scabini"><name
                                ref="Adalfredus">Adalfridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Scabini">schabinus</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Teobaldus">Teopaldo</name></persName>. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p>ChLA, 84, n. 25, 91-93; MDL, 4/2, n. 43, p. 59; 5/2, n. 888, p. 543</p>
            </div>
